Usage: saveTimingBudget [-help] [-dir <string>] [-module_model_tag <string>] [ -inst <string> | -ptn <string> ]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-dir <string>                   # output directory (string, optional)
-inst <string>                  # to specify instance list (string, optional)
-module_model_tag <string>      # Specifies module model tag to be used
                                # (string, optional)
-ptn <string>                   # to specify ptn list (string, optional)